<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Most groups wont let you do this, but if you find one that will it is a HUGE help in a camp where caster mobs are infrequent.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
